MobileResponderRecallNoticeTaskAttachmentForm is a Form
    title is "CommentsAndAttachments"
    restrict action MobileCreate
    Actions
        action is save
        action is previous record
        action is next record
        action is refresh
    Layout
        display as text
            paragraph
                RecallNotice
                RecallNotice.Name
        single column
            Title
            Comment
        paragraph
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                Attachment.Title
            Attachment.File
                label is "Attachment"
